text.tspan: Based on the expert estimates and index by V-Dem, weighted by countries' populations. It combines information
on voting rights, the freedom and fairness of elections, freedoms of association and expression, civil liberties, and
executive constraints. It ranges from 0 to 1 (most democratic).
